rComments: Best prof in environmental science - makes this course enjoyable for all students.  This is a tough course so listen to what she says about timing or you'll end up without enough time to finish your papers.

She has no love for teaching. Does not connect with students. Is not interested in helping those who struggle or just want some extra explanation. Why does she keep office hours if she is so disinterested anyway?

The final is a killer!  The exam should be cut down because it's alot of writing; one of the most intense in my University experience.  A ton of memorization & Yes the chemistry component is hard 4 those weak in this area.  Labs bring up the mark.  Don't need the book for this course.  The lec is also quite boring but well explained

Da class is very hard esp for those not good w chem!  There's alot of application of knowledge & memorization.  The exam should be cut down, it's too long.  The labs are o.k they help boost up marks.  This class is hard!
she was okay... her exams are tough. her final is very hard... its alot of application
